# Frontend UI Review Checklist

<!-- N/A — this project has no frontend (yet). Replace when applicable. -->

Use for any UI change; accessibility and performance checks.

- [ ] All interactive elements keyboard-navigable
- [ ] Color contrast meets WCAG 2.0 AA (4.5:1 for text, 3:1 for large text)
- [ ] Focus indicators visible on all interactive elements
- [ ] Images have descriptive alt text; decorative images have `alt=""`
- [ ] No layout shift on initial load (CLS < 0.1)
- [ ] Core Web Vitals within acceptable range (LCP < 2.5s, FID < 100ms)
- [ ] Responsive at 320px, 768px, 1280px breakpoints

